John chapter 1 verse 17 For the law was given through moses ( A servant ) but Grace and Truth came through Jesus Christ. ( The Son ) Notice how TRUTH is on the side of GRACE. There has been a change. A NEW COVENANT. Philippians chapter 3 verse 9 I no longer count on my own righteousness through obeying the law; rather, I become righteous through faith in Christ. For God's way of making us right with Himself depends on faith. Placing the new wine of the new covenant into the old wineskins of the old covenant you lose both.
